\f0\b0  Participants received a validated automated home blood pressure monitor and standardized training on proper measurement techniques. They were instructed to measure blood pressure twice daily (morning and evening) for at least five days per week and to record readings in a logbook. Readings were reviewed during follow-up visits.\
