\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 Statistical Analysis\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Data were analyzed using an intention-to-treat approach. Continuous variables were expressed as mean \'b1 standard deviation, and categorical variables as percentages. Between-group comparisons were performed using independent t-tests or chi-square tests as appropriate. A p-value < 0.05 was considered statistically significant.\
